  			<div id="item-3391"><p>That&#8217;s hilarious. It reminds me of those horrible, sugary cereals that pretend to be &#8220;part of a balanced breakfast,&#8221; when in fact you&#8217;d be better off not eating at all.</p>
<p>I had a similar private chuckle on Monday morning in the airport when I ate a McGriddle (my first one! and it wasn&#8217;t even that good). The bag, which was soaked through with grease from the sandwich and its accompanying hashbrown, was covered with scary illustrations of healthy people exercising and doing yoga. I&#8217;m thinking, these people are <em>not</em> have a McGriddle every morning.</p></div>
